Definition: a problematic situation that will eventually become dangerous if not addressed
Example: India is a demographic time bomb; the refugee camp is a ticking bomb waiting to go off
Synonyms: ticking_bomb, situation, a, problematic, that, will, eventually, become, dangerous, if, not, addressed, India, is, demographic, time, bomb, the, refugee, camp, ticking, waiting, to, go, off
Category: noun.state
